		<title>寵物醫療費飆漲！「寵星」助飼主預防重於治療</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/10/05/%e5%af%b5%e7%89%a9%e9%86%ab%e7%99%82%e8%b2%bb%e9%a3%86%e6%bc%b2%ef%bc%81%e3%80%8c%e5%af%b5%e6%98%9f%e3%80%8d%e5%8a%a9%e9%a3%bc%e4%b8%bb%e9%a0%90%e9%98%b2%e9%87%8d%e6%96%bc%e6%b2%bb%e7%99%82/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Sun, 05 Oct 2025 09:49:40 +0000</pubDate>
